{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6676e3c8ce","title":"在天安门城楼上和北大附中红卫兵谈话纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"29c6b3612f","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"6676e3c8ce"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"524cf57035","type":"title","text":"在天安门城楼上和北大附中红卫兵谈话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"99dbb66496","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：陆平现在干什么","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"66ae929f7e","type":"paragraph","text":"口口口：陆平在北大扫地","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"25977f51e2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：陆平只能扫地，就像我一样，我到了你们学校也只能扫扫地，别的干不来，我是你们的勤务员。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"ecdafadc47","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：张承先也是个环人，把你们红旗拆散了，你们要把红旗拉起来。你们发展多少人啦？","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"6246e4e514","type":"paragraph","text":"口口口：文发展了。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"ff2c1ff293","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这就对头了。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"d3f8d225cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口口问主席身体好不好）","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"af96ce4002","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我身体很好，我去长江里游泳，有个青年同志肝疼了，我就上来了。要不然可以游三四个小时。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"50e06d3af5","type":"paragraph","text":"（口口口问主席下一步应怎么办？）","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"f4c6f632e4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们一斗二批三改，按十六条办事。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"f7bd410f29","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛问口口口是否会游泳）","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"7b934c1b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"口口口：才学会，游得不好，只会游十几米。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"522f89c438","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那不叫游泳，那叫闲庭信步。（毛做了闲庭信步的动作）你要能这样，就从必然王国到自由王国了。你们老怕别人批评，马克思主义就是压出来的，经风雨，发展兴旺起来","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"a21c30fcec","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不能让她出风头，要让她谦虚","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"},{"id":"8872a9e20b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你怎么能这样说呢？要让人家革命嘛！","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce"}],"page":{"id":"b9d170b18b","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"6676e3c8ce","start":511,"end":512}}}},"__N_SSG":true}